<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>169</hymn_number>
<title>Kóktem keldi aınala qulpyryp РӘЖ169</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.    Dm               Gm
 Kóktem keldi aınala qulpyryp,
.          Dm A
 jer jasylyn jamylyp.
.  Dm                Gm
 Qustar keldi, ándete sán quryp,
.        Gm    A      Dm
 kóktemgi kún jylynyp.

[C1]
.   Gm      C      F       Bb
   Qýanyshty sonda habar estildi,
.   Gm     A          Dm
   Iem Isa tirildi! tirildi!
.    Gm   C     F     Bb
   Qýanyshty sonda habar estildi,
.   Gm     A          Dm
   Iem Isa tirildi, tirildi!

[V2]
 Qudiretti isi bul Qudaıdyń,
 eski jylan ezildi.
 Qudaı uly Másih ólip, tirilip,
 ómir jeńdi ólimdi.

[V3]
 Bar álemdi ólimnen qutqaryp,
 máńgi ómir syılady.
 Kıeli Rýh jan - dúnıemdi aqtaryp,
 jańa ómir bastaldy.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
</song>